Invocation Name: self help
des:
The Self Help skill finds the most popular self-help articles on the web and reads them to you. Think of it like audible but for the web, and free!

Just say "Start self help" and she'll start reading the most popular articles to you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
